  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support ventricular assist device hemolysis prediction using CFD. The credibility assessment covers the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD operating conditions. Thirteen credibility factors are evaluated at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors are assessed with achieved levels documented against required levels; six factors are flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. The package is submitted under the Minimal profile, which does not require a structured Context of Use block; intended-use scope is conveyed only through this narrative description.",
