      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics including validation uncertainty must be reported at Gradation 4, with agreement within defined acceptance bands.",
      "rationale": "Output comparison uses qualitative overlay plots without formal validation uncertainty estimation. The achieved level 2 does not satisfy the quantitative requirement at level 4."
