      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted under conditions sufficiently similar to the intended use environment to support extrapolation at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark pump geometry under idealized in-vitro conditions. Patient-specific VAD operating envelopes differ substantially; relevance gap is unmitigated."
    },
