      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical solver error must be bounded through iterative convergence analysis and round-off error assessment at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Solver error assessment was not performed. Residual convergence criteria are documented but no formal bounding of iterative or round-off error has been carried out. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
