      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty must be characterized through alternative model comparison or sensitivity analysis at Gradation 5 for MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model was adopted without comparison to alternative constitutive forms. Model form uncertainty is entirely uncharacterized. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
