      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions must be demonstrated quantitatively at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis was performed between CFD boundary conditions and experimental setup parameters. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
