    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all thirteen factors under the Minimal profile submission. While six factors remain unassessed and seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels, the submission is accepted under the Minimal profile requirements for the purposes of this package. The narrative description indicates this model has been applied in clinical research; however, no structured Context of Use is provided in this package, leaving the formal intended-use scope undefined. Acceptance is conditional on completion of outstanding factor assessments prior to regulatory submission.",
